    "_postman_id": "mypay-wallets-merchant-api-2026",
    "name": "MyPay Wallets - Merchant API",
    "description": "**MyPay Wallets Platform - Merchant API Collection**\n\n## Overview\nMyPay provides a unified API for wallet payments in Pakistan.\n\n## Base URLs\n\n### Production\n- **Unified**: https://wallets.mypay.mx/api/v1\n\n### Local Development\n- **Easypaisa**: http://localhost:4003/api/v1\n- **JazzCash**: http://localhost:4004/api/v1\n\n## Authentication\n\nHeader: `X-Api-Key`\n- Test Key: `test-wallets-key`\n- Production: Contact support@mypay.mx\n\n## Request Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"reference\": \"YOUR-ORDER-REF\",\n  \"amount\": 100.00,\n  \"mobile\": \"03XXXXXXXXX\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"easypaisa|jazzcash\"\n}\n```\n\n## Response Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true/false,\n  \"reference\": \"YOUR-ORDER-REF\",\n  \"status\": \"SUCCESS|PENDING|FAILED\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"easypaisa|jazzcash\",\n  \"amount\": 100.00,\n  \"currency\": \"PKR\",\n  \"transactionId\": \"PROVIDER_TXN_ID\"\n}\n```\n\n## Status Codes\n\n- 200: Transaction successful\n- 202: Pending (awaiting customer confirmation)\n- 400: Bad request or transaction failed\n- 401: Invalid/missing API key\n\n## Test Data\n\n- Mobile: 03097524704\n- Amount: PKR 5 (recommended for testing)\n\n**Version**: 2.0.0",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": {
      "major": 2,
      "minor": 0,
      "patch": 0
    }
  },
