            "description": "**Initiate Easypaisa Payment (Local)**\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `reference` | string | Yes | Your unique order reference |\n| `amount` | number | Yes | Amount in PKR (must be > 0) |\n| `mobile` | string | Yes | Customer mobile number (03XXXXXXXXX) |\n| `paymentMethod` | string | Yes | Must be \"easypaisa\" |\n\n### Response Statuses\n\n- **SUCCESS** (200): Payment completed\n- **PENDING** (202): Awaiting customer confirmation\n- **FAILED** (400): Payment rejected"
